external_knowledge:
- Top 5 highest-paid majors refers to the top 5 majors with the highest average salaries in 2022, as per the employment data; 
- The employment data is assumed to be based on recent statistics available up to 2022; 
- The ranks are assigned based on the average salaries for each major; 
- The query considers all types of employment sectors (Government, Private, Non-profit).

sql:
SELECT AVG(job_satisfaction) AS average_job_satisfaction
FROM job_outcomes
WHERE major_id = 0 AND year = 2022;

SELECT major_name, average_completion_time
FROM majors
WHERE availability = 'Yes';

SELECT major_name
FROM majors
ORDER BY major_name;
